BCL's double.IsNaN  got faster long ago. In .NET Core it is a single instruction.

The usage of [DoubleUti.IsNaN](https://github.com/dotnet/wpf/blob/7e118beef92050c247fac7ad24ce0816e42e77b6/src/Microsoft.DotNet.Wpf/src/Shared/MS/Internal/DoubleUtil.cs#L303) should be replaced by [double.IsNaN](https://github.com/dotnet/runtime/blob/4f8be1992cc79807d377afce640f219d4caffb5b/src/libraries/System.Private.CoreLib/src/System/Double.cs#L91).

[Codegen difference](https://sharplab.io/#v2:)


